data.description: Peaceful and serene describes this lovely home.  Featuring vaulted ceilings in a large open living and dining room area along with the updated kitchen with granite counter tops will make this your perfect 2nd or retirement home. With two bedrooms and two bathrooms, it is spacious with 1573 sq ft, plus a separate office/laundry room. Gorgeous Brazilian cherry wood flooring throughout, this home is tastefully decorated and meticulously kept.  Entertain on the large screened in Lanai overlooking the manicured backyard. Located on the east side of the street.  This well built home had the roof replaced in 2018 and is elevated above flood.  Walking distance to Cabana Club (ask us about their membership) and restaurants. Call now to see this beautiful home. Every night, drift off to sleep to the subtle sounds of the southeast breezes, then wake up to a spectacular sunrise over the Ocean. All of this is situated in Key Colony Beach, a convenient, friendly neighborhood only minutes away from grocery stores, restaurants, bars, fishing, diving, snorkeling and all water sports.  Close to Fishermen's Baptist medical facilities, Marathon Airport, library, Home Depot, including Hawks Cay Resort. Enjoy your morning walk to Sunset Park, and enjoy golf, tennis and pickleball around the corner.  Located in the Heart of Florida Keys North of Key West International Airport and South of Miami International Airport. Insurance premiums: Flood $1,040 and Wind $4,321.
